  "title": "Network and Security Engineer",
  "description": "<p><strong>KeyResponsibilities</strong><br /><br />Security Implementation & Management:</p><ul><li>Deploy and maintain F5 system with experience in LTM, WAF, API</li><li>Deploy and maintain Azure Cloud security with experience in APIM gateways</li><li>Implementation, and maintenance of network security solutions, with focus on Cisco FTD, FMC and Firewalls.</li></ul><p><br />Security Policy & Configuration:</p><p><ul><li>Implement, and enforce granular security policies on F5 ,firewalls and APIM gateways</li></ul><ul><li>Perform regular security policy rule base reviews, cleanups, and optimization to ensure a strong security posture and network performance.</li><li>Integrate and configure F5 solutions to enforce application delivery and security policies, including rules.</li></ul><p><br />Documentation & Collaboration:</p><ul><li>Documentation for diagrams. configurations, and standard operating procedures.</li></ul><ul><li>Collaborate closely with cross-functional teams to ensure security policies align with business objectives.</li></ul></p><p></p><p><strong>Qualifications</strong><br /><br /><strong>Experience</strong>: Minimum of 3-5 years of hands-on experience in a network security or engineering role.</p><p><br /><strong>Technical Skills</strong>:</p><ul><li>Proven experience with Azure cloud platforms security, including <strong>NSG</strong> and<strong> APIM</strong></li><li>Implementation knowledge of firewall solution and management security, including <strong>FTD</strong> and <strong>FMC</strong>.</li><li>Strong understanding of network protocols (TCP/IP, DNS, HTTP/S) and security principles (firewalls, IDS/IPS, VPNs).</li><li>Familiarity with automation, cloud security is a plus.</li></ul><p><br /><strong>Certifications (Preferred)</strong></p><ul><li>Microsoft Certified: Azure Security Engineer Associate</li><li>Cisco Certified Network Professional (CCNP) Security</li><li>F5 Certified Administrator or F5 Certified Technology Specialist (CTS).</li><li>Other security certifications like CISSP or CompTIA Security+ are a plus.</li></ul><p><br />EA License No.: 96C4864</p><p>Reg No.: R25128798 HUANG QIMENG</p>",
